Build and Installation of Anthy
							-*- text -*-

From source tar ball
--------------------

As with other packages, you just have to do

  $ ./configure
  $ make
  $ make install

(Before doing install you might need to become root.)


From Git repository (master branch)
-----------------------------------

Libtool, Automake, Autoconf are required.

  $ ./autogen.sh
  $ ./configure --enable-maintainer-mode
  $ make
  $ make install

(Before doing install you might need to become root.)

Make release tarball from Git repository (master branch)
---------------------------------------------------------

Libtool, Automake, Autoconf are required.

  * Bump release version in configure.ac
  * Update ChangeLog with updateLog.sh
  * Commit all to git repo

Then:
  $ ./autogen.sh
  $ ./configure --enable-maintainer-mode
  $ make
  $ make dist

-- 
